Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,「門」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走  魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真奧哥…
